        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Big Cat Public Safety Act</b></p> <p>This bill revises restrictions on the possession, exhibition, or breeding of big cats (i.e., species of lion, tiger, leopard, cheetah, jaguar, or cougar or any hybrid of such species). For example, the bill permits wildlife sanctuaries to allow direct contact between the public and big cats.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
